12346115.name: Juodasis kelias / Чорны тракт
12346115.description: Historical \"Black route\" between Vilnius (Lithuania) and Soły (Belarus). Comprises: almost all the Vilnius-Šumskas road; the Łoša-Stancyja Hudahaj road, but also smaller roads and tracks between St. Hudahaj & St. Ašmiany

12347827.name: Batoro traktas / тракт Баторыя
12347827.description: Historical route named after Stephen Báthory betweeen Vilnius (Lithuania) and Połack (Belarus). Leads through Naujoji Vilnia - Mickūnai - Lavoriškės - Słabada - Symaneli - Michališki - Svir - Kanstancinava - Duniłavičy and Hłybokaje

12430846.name: Napoleono traktas / Напалеонаўскі тракт
12430846.description: Historical route between Vilnius and Maładziečna. Goes through the old Vilnius Ašmiany route, Smarhoń and Lebedzieva,
